---
title: Roasted Carrot Dal with Cumin Spiced Chapatis
description: A dal is a delicious way to enjoy a large dose of veggies for dinner. This dal is made with lentils, spinach and delicious chantenay carrots. These little carrots are packed full of flavour and nutrients, and are a tasty addition to this Indian dish. As if this wasn't enough, we have also included cheat's chapatis, which make the best little shovels to scoop up your dal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-carrot-dal-4e94a07c-825e6028.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roasted-carrot-dal-5a90623bae08b54238638222-d1238313.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 640 kcal
  fat: 13 g
  saturated fat: 4 g
